1
00:01:35,860 --> 00:01:38,250
[Too Young To Love]

2
00:01:38,590 --> 00:01:41,289
[Episode 22]

3
00:01:43,620 --> 00:01:44,850
Tell me the truth.

4
00:01:45,250 --> 00:01:47,710
Will you get back together
with Tong Xiaole?

5
00:01:50,020 --> 00:01:50,759
No.

6
00:01:52,259 --> 00:01:52,960
Fine.

7
00:01:53,490 --> 00:01:55,190
If you hadn't returned to China for him,

8
00:01:55,190 --> 00:01:57,009
you wouldn't have missed
the graduation exam

9
00:01:57,009 --> 00:01:58,150
and still be stuck here now.

10
00:01:58,150 --> 00:01:58,789
Lan.

11
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,480
I'm done with my rehearsal.

12
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,720
It's your turn to go on stage.

13
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:04,550
Xiaole has been missing for over 10 days.

14
00:02:04,550 --> 00:02:05,660
I checked the flights.

15
00:02:05,660 --> 00:02:07,210
There's one last flight tonight.

16
00:02:07,210 --> 00:02:08,470
I'm going back right now.

17
00:02:08,470 --> 00:02:09,720
What about your exam?

18
00:02:10,870 --> 00:02:12,270
I'll figure it out later.

19
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,560
All right.

20
00:02:17,620 --> 00:02:18,560
As for the school and the teachers,

21
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:20,360
I'll try to put in a good word for you.

22
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:20,850
Okay.

23
00:02:23,190 --> 00:02:24,240
Xiaole is a grown man.

24
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,680
He'll be fine.

25
00:02:25,700 --> 00:02:26,900
Don't worry too much.

26
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,240
Stay safe.

27
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:31,680
Is Xiaole here?

28
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:32,970
I haven't been able to reach him.

29
00:02:32,970 --> 00:02:33,510
Xiaole...

30
00:02:33,510 --> 00:02:34,710
Xiaole went abroad for a shoot.

31
00:02:34,710 --> 00:02:35,910
He didn't tell you?

32
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:37,190
He went abroad?

33
00:02:38,790 --> 00:02:40,910
Maybe the signal isn't good over there.

34
00:02:40,910 --> 00:02:43,910
♪ By not thinking about it or guessing ♪

35
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:47,350
♪ I thought I could break free ♪

36
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:53,780
♪ Time has shown
I'm not as carefree as I imagined ♪

37
00:02:55,990 --> 00:02:59,950
♪ I still can't forget the tenderness
you gave me that year ♪

38
00:02:56,990 --> 00:02:58,320
You went looking for me?

39
00:02:58,390 --> 00:02:59,740
Are you still in China?

40
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:03,660
♪ Exhausting all my strength,
I still can't fool myself ♪

41
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,920
I didn't tell you
because I didn't want you to worry.

42
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:04,360
I'll come to see you in a couple of days.

43
00:03:04,140 --> 00:03:07,210
♪ Your place is still here ♪

44
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,800
You'll have your exams soon, right?

45
00:03:07,460 --> 00:03:11,200
♪ No one else can take it ♪

46
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:15,550
♪ Let me treat it as just a heavy rain ♪

47
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:20,370
♪ Gradually, the memories we've built
become clear ♪

48
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:18,110
I selfishly long for happiness.

49
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,540
I've realized the only way

50
00:03:20,530 --> 00:03:24,840
♪ All composed into a song ♪

51
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:22,390
for me to find myself again is

52
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:24,710
to leave you.

53
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:29,150
♪ It's still so beautiful ♪

54
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:34,790
What if you didn't want to come back,

55
00:03:34,790 --> 00:03:36,720
and he didn't want to go abroad?

56
00:03:41,980 --> 00:03:42,780
But I think

57
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:44,920
if we were in that situation,

58
00:03:45,310 --> 00:03:46,250
it wouldn't be like that.

59
00:03:46,250 --> 00:03:47,640
I would definitely take the initiative
and tell you

60
00:03:46,390 --> 00:03:49,829
♪ Every warm touch that drew us closer ♪

61
00:03:47,670 --> 00:03:49,590
I like you very, very, very much.

62
00:03:50,610 --> 00:03:52,630
♪ Was nothing but a dream ♪

63
00:03:51,290 --> 00:03:54,550
And I like you
very, very, very, very much.

64
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:56,570
♪ So many sunrises and sunsets ♪

65
00:03:56,829 --> 00:04:00,540
♪ Have changed our original hearts ♪

66
00:03:57,230 --> 00:04:00,570
Besides, you'll never
have a chance to do that in your life.

67
00:04:01,550 --> 00:04:04,790
♪ By not thinking about it or guessing ♪

68
00:04:04,860 --> 00:04:08,020
♪ I thought I could break free ♪

69
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:14,730
♪ Time has shown
I'm not as carefree as I imagined ♪

70
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:15,610
It's actually pretty nice to stay here.

71
00:04:15,610 --> 00:04:17,010
I really like this place.

72
00:04:17,459 --> 00:04:18,750
There are also a lot of Chinese people.

73
00:04:18,750 --> 00:04:21,550
And it gives me an extra year
to practice the cello.

74
00:04:21,890 --> 00:04:22,880
There are still so many things

75
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:24,680
I want to do but haven't done yet.

76
00:04:24,740 --> 00:04:26,150
You're quite optimistic.

77
00:04:26,150 --> 00:04:27,110
What if this year

78
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:28,040
you fail again?

79
00:04:29,090 --> 00:04:30,210
If I fail,

80
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:31,640
I'll try again next year.

81
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:33,170
At worst,

82
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,040
I'll just be a bit slower.

83
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:34,600
Anyway,

84
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:36,710
I'll reach the finish line eventually.

85
00:04:36,710 --> 00:04:37,570
What about you?

86
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:40,220
Are you really planning
to go back to China?

87
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,690
Although Fan hasn't told me explicitly,

88
00:04:43,690 --> 00:04:45,090
I know he wants to go back.

89
00:04:45,180 --> 00:04:46,050
Plus, his parents

90
00:04:46,050 --> 00:04:47,980
have urged him 5 or 6 times already.

91
00:04:48,490 --> 00:04:50,390
My dad and he want me

92
00:04:50,420 --> 00:04:52,420
to start an orchestra back in China.

93
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:54,159
Like you said, just let it be.

94
00:04:54,340 --> 00:04:55,670
That suits me just fine.

95
00:04:56,340 --> 00:04:57,580
An orchestra?

96
00:04:58,520 --> 00:04:59,770
Is there a spot for me?

97
00:04:59,820 --> 00:05:00,880
Save a place for me.

98
00:05:02,230 --> 00:05:04,330
My standards are very strict.

99
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,090
You may never

100
00:05:05,190 --> 00:05:06,160
get to be

101
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,490
the principal cellist.

102
00:05:07,830 --> 00:05:08,660
So what?

103
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,810
I'll be your backup.

104
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,320
But no matter what,

105
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,710
if I ever do a cello duet

106
00:05:14,710 --> 00:05:15,830
in the future,

107
00:05:16,250 --> 00:05:17,250
the other spot

108
00:05:17,570 --> 00:05:18,630
will only be yours.

109
00:05:18,750 --> 00:05:19,390
Always.

110
00:05:20,030 --> 00:05:21,330
Ning and I

111
00:05:21,450 --> 00:05:23,570
took very good care of Yi Lan.

112
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:25,480
What are your plans?

113
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,480
I can

114
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,920
give you some advice.

115
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:31,390
What plans do you think

116
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:34,060
I could possibly have now?

117
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,240
You can fool others,

118
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,390
but you can't fool me.

119
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:40,190
I know

120
00:05:40,690 --> 00:05:42,020
you can't just let it go.

121
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,409
Has she mentioned to you

122
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,730
what she plans to do

123
00:05:47,730 --> 00:05:49,090
after graduation?

124
00:05:50,860 --> 00:05:52,590
I haven't heard her mention it.

125
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,190
But regarding this,

126
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:54,560
we'll just

127
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,240
have to wait

128
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,480
until she successfully graduates

129
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,080
this year.

130
00:05:58,380 --> 00:05:59,730
But speaking of which,

131
00:05:59,750 --> 00:06:01,680
where on earth did you go last year?

132
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:02,920
To look for you,

133
00:06:02,950 --> 00:06:04,720
she skipped her graduation exam

134
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,520
and went straight back to China.

135
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,130
Back then,

136
00:06:10,220 --> 00:06:11,560
I went to snowy mountains.

137
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,170
There was no signal.

138
00:06:12,170 --> 00:06:13,140
No signal...

139
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:16,750
You really have a habit of disappearing,

140
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:17,550
Tong Xiaole.

141
00:06:17,570 --> 00:06:19,030
I really have to scold you.

142
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:20,710
Work is important,

143
00:06:20,740 --> 00:06:21,950
but it's just work.

144
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:22,730
You have a mouth.

145
00:06:22,730 --> 00:06:24,660
Couldn't you have told us earlier?

146
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:28,010
That was my fault.

147
00:06:29,420 --> 00:06:31,480
But it's too late to say anything now.

148
00:06:33,420 --> 00:06:34,530
I've decided.

149
00:06:35,570 --> 00:06:37,170
After this last exhibition,

150
00:06:37,180 --> 00:06:37,909
I'm done.

151
00:06:39,610 --> 00:06:42,010
Do you think
we can still get back together?

152
00:06:43,650 --> 00:06:44,460
Alright.

153
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,000
Getting back together?

154
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,060
About getting back together,

155
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:48,060
I am experienced.

156
00:06:48,110 --> 00:06:49,210
Let me tell you.

157
00:06:49,659 --> 00:06:51,170
You must stay calm.

158
00:06:51,190 --> 00:06:52,520
Don't act impulsively.

159
00:06:53,230 --> 00:06:54,430
You're experienced?

160
00:06:55,830 --> 00:06:57,290
When you got back together,

161
00:06:57,290 --> 00:06:58,820
who gave you the advice?

162
00:06:59,820 --> 00:07:00,570
I have practical experience.

163
00:07:00,570 --> 00:07:01,430
What about you?

164
00:07:02,790 --> 00:07:03,230
Fine.

165
00:07:03,380 --> 00:07:04,720
Let's stop talking about me.

166
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,450
You don't even write songs anymore.

167
00:07:06,450 --> 00:07:07,910
You just stay up all night playing games.

168
00:07:07,910 --> 00:07:09,610
You're going to ruin yourself
if this goes on.

169
00:07:09,610 --> 00:07:10,870
Mind your own business.

170
00:07:10,870 --> 00:07:12,390
I'm just enjoying life.

171
00:07:12,410 --> 00:07:13,240
Besides,

172
00:07:14,490 --> 00:07:15,640
I'm already rich.

173
00:07:16,030 --> 00:07:16,790
And

174
00:07:17,330 --> 00:07:18,420
now Ning

175
00:07:18,900 --> 00:07:19,990
earns a lot.

176
00:07:20,690 --> 00:07:22,450
Unlike someone

177
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:24,880
who can't even afford to buy a drink,

178
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:26,450
she can even support me.

179
00:07:29,370 --> 00:07:30,810
Like I said,

180
00:07:31,470 --> 00:07:33,080
I really envy your life.

181
00:07:37,340 --> 00:07:39,540
There are many ways to live.

182
00:07:40,180 --> 00:07:40,830
One is

183
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,170
for your dreams.

184
00:07:42,650 --> 00:07:43,300
Another is

185
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,010
for love.

186
00:07:46,010 --> 00:07:47,500
A happy family

187
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:49,870
always needs someone
to make sacrifices and compromises.

188
00:07:49,870 --> 00:07:50,870
Coincidentally,

189
00:07:51,130 --> 00:07:53,080
I happen to be willing

190
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:55,020
to sacrifice and compromise.

191
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:57,170
Alright.

192
00:07:57,190 --> 00:07:57,980
Hurry up and buy the drinks.

193
00:07:57,980 --> 00:07:59,909
I'm tired of your little speeches.

194
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,680
It's a video call.

195
00:08:09,180 --> 00:08:09,860
Mengmeng.

196
00:08:13,090 --> 00:08:13,940
Mengmeng.

197
00:08:14,770 --> 00:08:16,050
Lan, Ning.

198
00:08:16,260 --> 00:08:17,850
I saw the video Chen Fan posted.

199
00:08:17,850 --> 00:08:19,180
You guys were having such a good time.

200
00:08:19,180 --> 00:08:20,470
I miss you guys so much.

201
00:08:21,050 --> 00:08:22,950
We miss you so much, too.

202
00:08:24,210 --> 00:08:25,330
Where are you?

203
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,290
Why is it so dark?

204
00:08:28,100 --> 00:08:29,360
Shan and Professor Ye

205
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,620
went abroad for a trip.

206
00:08:30,650 --> 00:08:32,150
They left the shop to me.

207
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:34,440
I thought I'd try something new

208
00:08:34,460 --> 00:08:35,390
and spruce it up.

209
00:08:36,630 --> 00:08:38,940
Look at you, quite the boss now.

210
00:08:41,409 --> 00:08:42,210
Are you alone?

211
00:08:42,230 --> 00:08:43,559
Where is Zhao Zhenghao?

212
00:08:43,679 --> 00:08:44,800
That guy and I

213
00:08:44,830 --> 00:08:45,660
just don't get along.

214
00:08:45,660 --> 00:08:46,480
We've broken up.

215
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,260
But it's fine.

216
00:08:47,260 --> 00:08:47,920
From now on,

217
00:08:47,930 --> 00:08:50,140
I'll focus entirely on my business

218
00:08:50,170 --> 00:08:51,480
to make lots of money.

219
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:52,730
Alright.

220
00:08:52,750 --> 00:08:53,650
I gotta get back to work now.

221
00:08:53,650 --> 00:08:54,650
Talk to you later.

222
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:55,340
Bye.

223
00:08:56,450 --> 00:08:57,450
Cheers, then.

224
00:08:58,990 --> 00:08:59,500
Bye.

225
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:00,090
Bye.

226
00:09:02,370 --> 00:09:03,340
So they broke up.

227
00:09:05,820 --> 00:09:06,590
Coming.

228
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:10,130
It's too cold outside.

229
00:09:10,820 --> 00:09:12,060
Sit here and warm up.

230
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:18,030
Book the tickets.

231
00:09:18,030 --> 00:09:18,990
We're going back to China next week.

232
00:09:18,990 --> 00:09:20,450
And we're not coming back.

233
00:09:21,070 --> 00:09:22,070
That's so sudden.

234
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,450
When did you decide this?

235
00:09:23,450 --> 00:09:24,280
Well,

236
00:09:24,310 --> 00:09:25,270
just now.

237
00:09:26,300 --> 00:09:28,100
Let's talk about this tomorrow.

238
00:09:28,490 --> 00:09:29,250
I'm serious.

239
00:09:29,270 --> 00:09:30,130
I'm not drunk.

240
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:32,380
-You're definitely drunk right now.
-Book the tickets.

241
00:09:32,380 --> 00:09:34,980
Otherwise I might regret it
and change my mind.

242
00:09:35,430 --> 00:09:36,160
Okay.

243
00:09:55,530 --> 00:09:56,430
To celebrate

244
00:09:56,460 --> 00:09:58,140
Fan and I returning to China next week,

245
00:09:58,140 --> 00:09:59,540
let's drink till we drop.

246
00:10:00,190 --> 00:10:01,250
Drink till we drop.

247
00:10:09,260 --> 00:10:10,160
Cheers.

248
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:14,310
[BLUES WORLD]

249
00:10:39,730 --> 00:10:43,520
♪ It's raining in my city, soft and slow ♪

250
00:10:43,910 --> 00:10:47,800
♪ As if you took all the sunshine with you
when you left ♪

251
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:51,870
♪ The old lanes we walked
are flooded with memories of us ♪

252
00:10:52,010 --> 00:10:55,810
♪ Now, I just stand here
as lovers brush past me ♪

253
00:10:56,340 --> 00:11:00,150
♪ Some remain forever young and free ♪

254
00:11:00,330 --> 00:11:04,430
♪ In their eyes, I see you and me ♪

255
00:11:04,510 --> 00:11:08,630
♪ The lonely air surrounds me ♪

256
00:11:09,130 --> 00:11:15,230
♪ Shutting out the noise
and all the warmth ♪

257
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:20,090
♪ I wish I could be a goldfish ♪

258
00:11:20,180 --> 00:11:24,030
♪ With its so-called seven-second memory ♪

259
00:11:24,300 --> 00:11:28,200
♪ Seven was the moment we first met,
and six was when we grew close ♪

260
00:11:28,460 --> 00:11:32,610
♪ Now, there's just an empty space
beside me where you should be ♪

261
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:34,270
[L Photography]

262
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,480
I've recently discovered

263
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:33,360
a super interesting social media account.

264
00:11:32,860 --> 00:11:36,520
♪ Just let me become a goldfish ♪

265
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:35,250
Look, this photo looks just like you.

266
00:11:35,250 --> 00:11:35,950
Me?

267
00:11:36,660 --> 00:11:38,230
Recently, I've been following
a photography blogger,

268
00:11:36,870 --> 00:11:40,180
♪ So I wouldn't be swallowed
by memories anymore ♪

269
00:11:38,250 --> 00:11:39,350
who is really amzaing.

270
00:11:39,350 --> 00:11:40,260
Mengmeng keeps saying

271
00:11:40,260 --> 00:11:41,600
this photo looks like me.

272
00:11:40,670 --> 00:11:44,590
♪ Five was all the hugs we shared,
and four was the moment we broke up ♪

273
00:11:43,090 --> 00:11:45,000
These are the breakfast place, the café,

274
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:45,710
and the streets

275
00:11:45,010 --> 00:11:49,120
♪ Three, two, one, and I can finally ♪

276
00:11:45,740 --> 00:11:46,420
we always go to.

277
00:11:46,420 --> 00:11:47,730
They're exactly the same
as the places we go to.

278
00:11:47,730 --> 00:11:49,080
He pinned the photo of this girl's back

279
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:49,750
to the top.

280
00:11:49,660 --> 00:11:52,580
♪ Forget you ♪

281
00:11:50,170 --> 00:11:51,640
Look at the hem of the school uniform.

282
00:11:51,640 --> 00:11:52,550
It's exactly the same as the hem

283
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:53,640
of our school uniform.

284
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:55,270
He has a secret crush on her.

285
00:11:58,430 --> 00:11:59,570
I noticed

286
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:01,580
that you had deleted my photo.

287
00:12:02,300 --> 00:12:04,560
Were you afraid of getting me in trouble?

288
00:12:05,230 --> 00:12:06,700
What you need to do now is

289
00:12:06,730 --> 00:12:08,340
get well-prepared

290
00:12:08,370 --> 00:12:09,710
for studying abroad.

291
00:12:28,550 --> 00:12:29,750
Xiaole, you're back.

292
00:12:29,810 --> 00:12:31,000
Mr. Yi, cleaning up?

293
00:12:33,910 --> 00:12:34,670
Be careful.

294
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:38,600
Mrs. Tong.

295
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:39,800
Tong.

296
00:12:41,510 --> 00:12:42,070
What's up?

297
00:12:42,070 --> 00:12:43,180
Why so happy?

298
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,150
Today is a good day.

299
00:12:45,150 --> 00:12:45,750
I'm going to park the car.

300
00:12:45,750 --> 00:12:46,400
Be careful.

301
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:47,040
Lan

302
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,060
has graduated.

303
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:48,830
Really?

304
00:12:48,850 --> 00:12:49,830
She's coming back today.

305
00:12:49,830 --> 00:12:50,620
Where is she?

306
00:12:50,930 --> 00:12:52,060
She'll be here soon.

307
00:12:53,160 --> 00:12:54,450
Xiaole went to pick you up.

308
00:12:54,450 --> 00:12:55,850
She wouldn't let me pick her up.

309
00:12:55,850 --> 00:12:57,510
I wonder who's picking her up.

310
00:12:58,060 --> 00:12:59,320
Look how happy you are.

311
00:12:59,380 --> 00:12:59,860
How is

312
00:12:59,890 --> 00:13:00,620
your health?

313
00:13:01,550 --> 00:13:01,940
You...

314
00:13:01,940 --> 00:13:02,680
No big problem.

315
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:03,830
You just can't get angry.

316
00:13:03,830 --> 00:13:05,630
Mrs. Tong, don't make him angry.

317
00:13:09,830 --> 00:13:10,280
Look.

318
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:11,480
For me?

319
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:12,390
Yes.

320
00:13:12,590 --> 00:13:13,130
Mr. Yi,

321
00:13:13,560 --> 00:13:16,360
you love practicing swordplay
in the morning, right?

322
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:17,260
Try this sword.

323
00:13:17,290 --> 00:13:18,560
Watch your mouth.

324
00:13:19,560 --> 00:13:20,610
It's a limited edition.

325
00:13:20,610 --> 00:13:22,340
It really is a limited edition.

326
00:13:22,530 --> 00:13:23,160
Look at this.

327
00:13:23,160 --> 00:13:23,640
Do you like it?

328
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:24,330
Your son

329
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:24,900
is so thoughtful.

330
00:13:24,900 --> 00:13:26,960
He's more thoughtful than any of you.

331
00:13:27,140 --> 00:13:28,050
I love it.

332
00:13:30,570 --> 00:13:31,050
Dad!

333
00:13:31,070 --> 00:13:31,970
Lan!

334
00:13:37,490 --> 00:13:39,200
I'm finally back.

335
00:13:39,380 --> 00:13:40,530
Come on.

336
00:13:40,910 --> 00:13:41,550
Be careful.

337
00:13:41,550 --> 00:13:43,480
-I missed you so much!
-Be careful.

338
00:13:44,050 --> 00:13:45,850
Dad, how come you have grey hair already?

339
00:13:45,850 --> 00:13:46,520
I got it

340
00:13:46,550 --> 00:13:47,240
from missing you.

341
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,030
Hello, Mr. Tong, Mrs. Tong.

342
00:13:48,030 --> 00:13:48,930
Lan.

343
00:13:52,250 --> 00:13:52,910
Your cello.

344
00:13:55,050 --> 00:13:57,180
Mr. Yi, you look so handsome and young.

345
00:13:58,190 --> 00:13:59,480
This is my friend from abroad,

346
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:00,200
Mark.

347
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:02,580
It's my pleasure to meet you.

348
00:14:03,300 --> 00:14:04,830
Your dad's English is good.

349
00:14:05,530 --> 00:14:06,460
You're here too?

350
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,040
It's my house.

351
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:09,560
Where else would I be?

352
00:14:10,110 --> 00:14:12,710
Well then, I won't take up
any more of your time.

353
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,320
I'll visit you when I'm free.

354
00:14:14,790 --> 00:14:15,340
Okay.

355
00:14:16,630 --> 00:14:17,370
Take care.

356
00:14:21,690 --> 00:14:22,470
Bye.

357
00:14:27,070 --> 00:14:28,550
Dad, it's a bit cold.

358
00:14:28,570 --> 00:14:29,700
Maybe we should go inside.

359
00:14:29,700 --> 00:14:30,320
Let's go inside quickly.

360
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,450
Mr. Tong, Mrs. Tong, I'm going in now.

361
00:14:31,450 --> 00:14:32,380
Take care.

362
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:35,330
Remember to come over for dinner tonight.

363
00:14:35,330 --> 00:14:35,870
Okay.

364
00:14:39,260 --> 00:14:40,300
You know that guy?

365
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:43,010
Well,

366
00:14:43,040 --> 00:14:44,840
he was a local guide I met abroad.

367
00:14:44,870 --> 00:14:45,890
During a dinner with Lan,

368
00:14:45,890 --> 00:14:46,690
I met him once.

369
00:14:57,610 --> 00:14:58,870
Aren't you cold?

370
00:15:01,570 --> 00:15:02,480
This is how I usually work out.

371
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:03,280
I'm used to it.

372
00:15:05,640 --> 00:15:07,300
You're so self-disciplined.

373
00:15:40,260 --> 00:15:41,460
Xiaole, you're here.

374
00:15:41,990 --> 00:15:42,500
Mr. Yi.

375
00:15:43,970 --> 00:15:44,950
You're cooking?

376
00:15:46,020 --> 00:15:47,140
I...

377
00:15:47,170 --> 00:15:48,410
I came by for dinner.

378
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:50,530
It's way too early for that.

379
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:52,330
Lan isn't home.

380
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:53,970
She went to the park for a walk.

381
00:15:53,970 --> 00:15:55,170
Go look for her there.

382
00:15:55,710 --> 00:15:56,350
And

383
00:15:56,370 --> 00:15:57,970
keep her company for a while.

384
00:15:57,990 --> 00:15:58,320
Okay.

385
00:15:58,340 --> 00:15:58,720
Then

386
00:15:58,830 --> 00:16:01,050
I won't stay any longer, Mr. Yi.

387
00:16:01,430 --> 00:16:02,280
Also...

388
00:16:03,890 --> 00:16:04,740
I know

389
00:16:05,190 --> 00:16:06,120
long-distance relationships

390
00:16:06,120 --> 00:16:07,920
make people drift apart easily.

391
00:16:08,630 --> 00:16:09,580
I also know

392
00:16:09,610 --> 00:16:10,870
how good you are to Lan.

393
00:16:11,050 --> 00:16:12,090
I've seen it.

394
00:16:12,220 --> 00:16:13,740
If you have any problems you can't solve,

395
00:16:13,740 --> 00:16:14,760
just tell me.

396
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:16,100
I'll help you fix them.

397
00:16:17,280 --> 00:16:17,790
It's okay.

398
00:16:17,790 --> 00:16:18,610
We're fine.

399
00:16:18,930 --> 00:16:19,530
It's okay?

400
00:16:20,140 --> 00:16:20,650
Alright.

401
00:16:20,650 --> 00:16:21,180
Go ahead.

402
00:16:21,610 --> 00:16:22,610
Hurry up.

403
00:16:22,640 --> 00:16:23,620
Off you go.

404
00:16:27,920 --> 00:16:28,430
Go.

405
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:30,180
Thanks, Mr. Yi.

406
00:16:36,410 --> 00:16:37,250
Sister,

407
00:16:38,680 --> 00:16:39,370
I'm here.

408
00:16:39,790 --> 00:16:41,120
You're finally here.

409
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:42,970
It smells so good.

410
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,740
I could smell it all the way here.

411
00:16:46,740 --> 00:16:48,000
I was craving it so bad.

412
00:16:48,060 --> 00:16:49,520
Sister, are these enough?

413
00:16:51,250 --> 00:16:51,640
Yes.

414
00:16:52,010 --> 00:16:53,040
Don't tell Dad.

415
00:16:53,060 --> 00:16:53,690
Don't worry.

416
00:16:53,690 --> 00:16:54,690
I won't say a word.

417
00:16:57,970 --> 00:16:59,000
You know what, Xuan?

418
00:16:59,000 --> 00:17:00,700
You look much bigger in person

419
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:02,190
than on video.

420
00:17:02,970 --> 00:17:03,490
Oh.

421
00:17:04,720 --> 00:17:05,410
And you're still laughing?

422
00:17:05,410 --> 00:17:06,339
Okay, I'll stop.

423
00:17:07,089 --> 00:17:07,569
Sister,

424
00:17:07,940 --> 00:17:08,890
do you know this?

425
00:17:08,980 --> 00:17:09,950
Mrs. Wang went to Xiaole's house

426
00:17:09,950 --> 00:17:10,839
every other day

427
00:17:10,859 --> 00:17:12,359
to play matchmaker.

428
00:17:13,030 --> 00:17:14,450
She was taking advantage of your absence.

429
00:17:14,450 --> 00:17:15,040
I've told her off

430
00:17:15,040 --> 00:17:16,500
to her face several times.

431
00:17:17,589 --> 00:17:19,930
Xiaole was not interested in any of them?

432
00:17:19,950 --> 00:17:20,910
He wouldn't dare!

433
00:17:20,910 --> 00:17:22,250
Sister, you're so wonderful.

434
00:17:22,250 --> 00:17:23,900
You know so much now.

435
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:25,730
Who taught you all this?

436
00:17:27,190 --> 00:17:28,790
Xiaole has been tutoring me.

437
00:17:30,200 --> 00:17:31,330
With Xiaole's help,

438
00:17:31,330 --> 00:17:32,920
I'll definitely get into a top university.

439
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:33,730
Stop bothering him

440
00:17:33,730 --> 00:17:35,020
so much, you hear?

441
00:17:35,050 --> 00:17:36,610
He has his own things to do.

442
00:17:36,630 --> 00:17:37,950
Okay, got it.

443
00:17:38,660 --> 00:17:39,140
Sister,

444
00:17:39,330 --> 00:17:41,320
when will you and Xiaole
finally get engaged?

445
00:17:41,320 --> 00:17:42,110
He has promised me

446
00:17:42,110 --> 00:17:43,270
that when you two get engaged,

447
00:17:43,270 --> 00:17:44,870
he'll give me his old camera.

448
00:17:45,810 --> 00:17:47,900
Why do you even want his old camera?

449
00:17:48,590 --> 00:17:49,440
To look cool.

450
00:17:49,560 --> 00:17:51,690
It'll make me very popular in college.

451
00:17:54,410 --> 00:17:55,190
Xiaole!

452
00:17:55,960 --> 00:17:56,480
Sister,

453
00:17:56,920 --> 00:17:57,310
before you go back home,

454
00:17:57,310 --> 00:17:58,510
remember to get the smell off you.

455
00:17:58,510 --> 00:17:59,440
I'm leaving now.

456
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:01,610
Xiaole, we have BBQ.

457
00:18:05,810 --> 00:18:07,140
I'm grabbing a few more.

458
00:18:07,420 --> 00:18:09,550
-Don't eat too much.
-Save some for me.

459
00:18:31,430 --> 00:18:32,020
Your...

460
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:33,550
Your dad told me you were here,

461
00:18:33,550 --> 00:18:34,480
so I just...

462
00:18:34,480 --> 00:18:35,720
c-came over.

463
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:36,790
Oh.

464
00:18:44,750 --> 00:18:45,700
Why didn't

465
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:47,870
the nougat vendor

466
00:18:47,890 --> 00:18:49,860
set up his stall today?

467
00:18:54,270 --> 00:18:55,550
His son

468
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:57,400
moved to a new school,

469
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:59,500
so he moved to a different spot.

470
00:19:07,100 --> 00:19:09,510
Are you seriously sneaking bites
right now?

471
00:19:09,510 --> 00:19:11,340
Uncle Dong made dinner at home.

472
00:19:11,360 --> 00:19:12,510
If you eat so much barbecue,

473
00:19:12,510 --> 00:19:13,900
you might be too full
to have dinner later.

474
00:19:13,900 --> 00:19:15,700
I haven't had BBQ here in so long.

475
00:19:15,830 --> 00:19:17,160
I just missed the taste.

476
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:18,570
Okay.

477
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:20,840
As long as you can finish
all that dinner later,

478
00:19:20,840 --> 00:19:21,790
it's fine.

479
00:19:24,590 --> 00:19:25,240
By the way,

480
00:19:25,830 --> 00:19:26,490
they said

481
00:19:26,520 --> 00:19:29,110
they want to get together
the day after tomorrow.

482
00:19:29,110 --> 00:19:30,170
Do you want to come?

483
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:31,240
Sure.

484
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:32,720
I want to see

485
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:33,920
Mengmeng and Ning.

486
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:37,880
Well,

487
00:19:38,110 --> 00:19:39,480
if they ask then,

488
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:41,640
what are you going to say?

489
00:19:43,340 --> 00:19:45,950
Ask about what?

490
00:19:50,240 --> 00:19:51,160
Us.

491
00:19:57,890 --> 00:19:59,480
We'll just say we broke up.

492
00:19:59,570 --> 00:20:00,860
Just tell the truth.

493
00:20:04,830 --> 00:20:06,160
Are you seeing someone?

494
00:20:09,240 --> 00:20:10,200
Are you?

495
00:20:17,130 --> 00:20:18,150
No.

496
00:20:18,590 --> 00:20:20,320
Why are you looking at me like that?

497
00:20:20,320 --> 00:20:21,670
Don't give me that look
the day after tomorrow.

498
00:20:21,670 --> 00:20:22,830
Otherwise, they'll get the wrong idea

499
00:20:22,830 --> 00:20:24,310
and think I dumped you.

500
00:20:26,770 --> 00:20:28,090
Isn't that the truth?

501
00:20:31,870 --> 00:20:33,030
What flavor is this?

502
00:20:34,270 --> 00:20:34,830
The same as yours.

503
00:20:34,830 --> 00:20:36,560
I've already taken a bite of it.

504
00:20:37,480 --> 00:20:38,400
Cumin flavor.

505
00:20:38,550 --> 00:20:39,480
And this is spicy flavor.

506
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:40,880
They're a perfect match.

507
00:20:44,070 --> 00:20:46,120
Let me see what other flavors there are.

508
00:20:46,120 --> 00:20:47,480
Just get the bags yourself.

509
00:20:47,480 --> 00:20:48,140
Why go

510
00:20:48,170 --> 00:20:48,990
the long way

511
00:20:49,010 --> 00:20:50,090
around me?

512
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:51,920
No, I...

513
00:20:51,940 --> 00:20:53,550
I just didn't want you to accuse me

514
00:20:53,550 --> 00:20:54,650
of sneaking food again.

515
00:20:54,650 --> 00:20:55,780
What the heck?

516
00:21:00,270 --> 00:21:00,830
Xiaole!

517
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:02,550
The light bulb at my home is broken.

518
00:21:02,550 --> 00:21:03,880
Can you help replace it?

519
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:05,310
Okay, Uncle Dong.

520
00:21:05,310 --> 00:21:06,570
I'll go buy one in a bit.

521
00:21:14,030 --> 00:21:14,810
Xiaole.

522
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:16,680
Xiaole!

523
00:21:17,790 --> 00:21:18,440
Xiaole!

524
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:19,210
What's up?

525
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:21,480
I'm going over to your place for tutoring.

526
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:22,740
Okay, the door is open.

527
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:33,170
Yi, go get the oil.

528
00:21:34,310 --> 00:21:35,200
Mrs. Yi,

529
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:37,240
I'm heading to the supermarket anyway.

530
00:21:37,240 --> 00:21:38,480
I'll bring it back for you.

531
00:21:38,480 --> 00:21:38,930
Okay.

532
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:39,620
No problem.

533
00:21:43,110 --> 00:21:43,920
Eat up.

534
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:45,210
Coming.

535
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:51,100
Let me tell you something.

536
00:21:51,830 --> 00:21:52,670
What is it?

537
00:21:52,880 --> 00:21:54,000
Announcing your marriage?

538
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:55,460
It can't happen that fast.

539
00:21:56,110 --> 00:21:57,570
You can get engaged first.

540
00:21:59,000 --> 00:22:01,260
Stop asking Tong Xiaole for help,

541
00:22:01,480 --> 00:22:02,140
okay?

542
00:22:03,510 --> 00:22:04,220
Sister,

543
00:22:04,440 --> 00:22:05,970
did Xiaole complain to you?

544
00:22:06,440 --> 00:22:07,680
You haven't even married him yet,

545
00:22:07,680 --> 00:22:09,680
and you're already taking his side?

546
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:11,440
Feeling sorry for Xiaole?

547
00:22:11,440 --> 00:22:12,510
I already said no,

548
00:22:12,720 --> 00:22:14,810
but Xiaole insisted on helping me.

549
00:22:15,110 --> 00:22:16,070
Anyway,

550
00:22:16,070 --> 00:22:17,640
just stop asking him for help.

551
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:18,270
Okay.

552
00:22:18,750 --> 00:22:19,550
We'll stop it.

553
00:22:20,480 --> 00:22:21,160
Mrs. Yi,

554
00:22:21,790 --> 00:22:23,720
I got the oil for you
from the supermarket.

555
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:24,680
I'll just put it in the kitchen.

556
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:25,840
Thank you, Xiaole.

557
00:22:26,000 --> 00:22:26,660
No problem.

558
00:22:29,800 --> 00:22:31,310
Mr. Yi, the light in the bathroom
is broken,

559
00:22:31,310 --> 00:22:32,620
so I bought you a couple of light bulbs.

560
00:22:32,620 --> 00:22:33,530
It's E14, right?

561
00:22:33,530 --> 00:22:33,840
Yes.

562
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:34,440
Okay.

563
00:22:34,550 --> 00:22:35,070
No rush.

564
00:22:35,070 --> 00:22:35,720
Change it later.

565
00:22:35,720 --> 00:22:36,580
Come eat first.

566
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:37,630
Okay.

567
00:22:37,650 --> 00:22:38,510
Come eat first.

568
00:22:38,590 --> 00:22:39,650
I'll wash my hands.

569
00:22:42,830 --> 00:22:44,720
What's with the feast?
You're eating like royalty.

570
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:45,800
Take a guess.

571
00:22:45,960 --> 00:22:47,070
Let me do it, Mr. Yi.

572
00:22:47,310 --> 00:22:48,000
Xiaole.

573
00:22:48,200 --> 00:22:48,510
Yeah?

574
00:22:48,510 --> 00:22:49,510
I'll go to your place later.

575
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:50,160
Sure.

576
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:52,480
You just want to play video games,
don't you?

577
00:22:52,480 --> 00:22:54,410
Xiaole, you must keep an eye on him.

578
00:22:54,750 --> 00:22:55,400
Mrs. Yi,

579
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:57,070
Xuan really has tutoring class tonight.

580
00:22:57,070 --> 00:22:58,070
Don't worry. I'll keep an eye on him.

581
00:22:58,070 --> 00:22:58,750
Exactly.

582
00:22:59,170 --> 00:23:00,390
Alright, I trust you.

583
00:23:00,880 --> 00:23:01,720
Come out with me.

584
00:23:01,720 --> 00:23:02,850
I need to talk to you.

585
00:23:03,060 --> 00:23:04,660
Let him have some food first.

586
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:06,480
He hasn't even finished his food yet.

587
00:23:06,480 --> 00:23:06,880
Yi Lan,

588
00:23:06,880 --> 00:23:08,110
slow down!

589
00:23:12,590 --> 00:23:13,000
So,

590
00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:14,480
no wonder

591
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:16,010
they're so grateful to you.

592
00:23:16,730 --> 00:23:17,210
Tell me.

593
00:23:17,720 --> 00:23:20,320
What were you really up to
by sucking up to them?

594
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,510
How was that sucking up to them?

595
00:23:22,510 --> 00:23:24,550
I was just giving them a hand
when I could.

596
00:23:24,550 --> 00:23:27,550
How come I've never seen you
helping other neighbors?

597
00:23:27,960 --> 00:23:29,160
Were you even in the country?

598
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:30,640
How do you know I didn't?

599
00:23:32,830 --> 00:23:33,520
It's just

600
00:23:33,640 --> 00:23:35,100
that you treat them so well.

601
00:23:35,100 --> 00:23:36,680
When they find out we've broken up,

602
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:39,340
-they're definitely going to be upset.
-Yi Lan!

603
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:41,410
Look at how old your dad is now.

604
00:23:41,480 --> 00:23:43,680
Last year he even fell and hurt his leg
just changing a light bulb.

605
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:44,920
Mrs. Yi has tenosynovitis in her hands.

606
00:23:44,920 --> 00:23:46,030
She can't lift heavy things now.

607
00:23:46,030 --> 00:23:46,660
Also,

608
00:23:46,720 --> 00:23:49,070
don't you want Xuan
to get into a good university?

609
00:23:49,070 --> 00:23:51,400
Besides, Xuan runs errands for me too.

610
00:23:54,990 --> 00:23:56,320
Anyway,

611
00:23:56,960 --> 00:23:58,550
I'm really grateful to you.

612
00:23:59,750 --> 00:24:00,550
Thank you.

613
00:24:03,750 --> 00:24:05,150
I'm just taking care
of my good friend's family.

614
00:24:05,150 --> 00:24:06,400
It's no big deal.

615
00:24:06,550 --> 00:24:08,350
Besides, after all these years,

616
00:24:09,000 --> 00:24:10,660
they're like family to me too.

617
00:24:11,880 --> 00:24:14,090
If you ever need anything from me,

618
00:24:14,240 --> 00:24:15,160
just say it.

619
00:24:16,400 --> 00:24:17,240
Don't worry.

620
00:24:17,720 --> 00:24:19,570
If I ever need your help,

621
00:24:19,680 --> 00:24:21,810
I definitely won't hesitate to say it.

622
00:24:28,590 --> 00:24:29,030
Hello.

623
00:24:30,570 --> 00:24:31,360
Mark.

624
00:24:32,880 --> 00:24:33,510
Anytime.

625
00:24:35,340 --> 00:24:36,410
How about

626
00:24:36,440 --> 00:24:37,110
tomorrow?

627
00:24:38,320 --> 00:24:38,750
Sure.

628
00:24:39,350 --> 00:24:41,280
I'll send you the time and address.

629
00:24:42,590 --> 00:24:43,590
See you tomorrow.

630
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:49,480
You remember
we have a get‑together tomorrow, right?

631
00:24:49,480 --> 00:24:50,480
Yeah, I remember.

632
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:51,690
Alright.

633
00:24:52,350 --> 00:24:54,350
Then get up early tomorrow morning.

634
00:24:55,510 --> 00:24:56,710
I'll come pick you up.

635
00:24:58,480 --> 00:24:59,280
No need.

636
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:08,500
It smells so good.

637
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:09,990
Lan.

638
00:25:10,400 --> 00:25:12,640
It has been a while
since you had my cooking, right?

639
00:25:12,640 --> 00:25:15,140
-Yeah. It has been a long time.
-Here it is.

640
00:25:15,140 --> 00:25:15,890
Put it here.

641
00:25:19,920 --> 00:25:20,750
When you were abroad,

642
00:25:20,750 --> 00:25:22,440
you only told us the good news
and never the bad.

643
00:25:22,440 --> 00:25:24,100
Just look how thin you've got.

644
00:25:25,920 --> 00:25:26,450
Eat more.

645
00:25:26,790 --> 00:25:27,680
Yeah.

646
00:25:27,920 --> 00:25:28,640
Remember

647
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:30,590
that health is the foundation
of everything.

648
00:25:30,590 --> 00:25:31,210
Got it?

649
00:25:31,310 --> 00:25:32,610
Dad, don't worry.

650
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:35,000
I've started working
and earning money now.

651
00:25:35,000 --> 00:25:36,590
There's no need to worry at all.

652
00:25:36,590 --> 00:25:38,190
Don't always pinch pennies.

653
00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:40,720
Eat more.

654
00:25:45,880 --> 00:25:46,930
Lan,

655
00:25:47,210 --> 00:25:49,480
your dad saw you lost weight abroad,

656
00:25:49,510 --> 00:25:50,480
so he put the meat in your bowl.

657
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:51,890
How can I eat it first?

658
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:52,920
I'm not hungry.

659
00:25:52,920 --> 00:25:53,920
Here, you have it.

660
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:00,650
It's delicious.

661
00:26:02,480 --> 00:26:03,520
Seeing you two

662
00:26:03,550 --> 00:26:04,590
getting along so well,

663
00:26:04,590 --> 00:26:05,590
I'm relieved.

664
00:26:07,510 --> 00:26:08,720
Dad, Auntie, you two eat too.

665
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:09,410
Okay.

666
00:26:09,550 --> 00:26:09,960
Xuan.

667
00:26:09,960 --> 00:26:10,310
Hurry and eat.

668
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:11,440
You should eat less.

669
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:12,500
Watch your intake.

670
00:26:12,970 --> 00:26:15,500
Look, even your sister
thinks you're too big.

671
00:26:15,500 --> 00:26:16,760
Xuan is still growing.

672
00:26:16,790 --> 00:26:17,850
Alright, alright.

673
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:21,070
This glass of beer...

674
00:26:21,070 --> 00:26:21,530
Xiaole.

675
00:26:23,000 --> 00:26:24,000
All these years,

676
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:26,160
everything you've done for our family…

677
00:26:26,160 --> 00:26:28,350
My wife and I have seen it all clearly.

678
00:26:29,650 --> 00:26:31,690
So I hope that you and Lan...

679
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:33,010
-Mr. Yi!
-You two...

680
00:26:35,950 --> 00:26:37,350
You're being too formal.

681
00:26:37,790 --> 00:26:39,720
All those years when Lan was abroad,

682
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:40,720
you were worried.

683
00:26:41,270 --> 00:26:43,330
I should be the one making a toast you.

684
00:26:46,610 --> 00:26:47,480
Alright.

685
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,370
Lan, let me tell you.

686
00:26:57,750 --> 00:26:58,400
You

687
00:26:58,920 --> 00:27:00,380
only came back once a year.

688
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:01,390
Xuan

689
00:27:02,550 --> 00:27:03,790
had classes every day.

690
00:27:03,790 --> 00:27:05,050
No one kept me company.

691
00:27:06,720 --> 00:27:08,050
Xiaole was really nice.

692
00:27:09,630 --> 00:27:11,560
He often came over to drink with me.

693
00:27:11,920 --> 00:27:12,830
So,

694
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:15,210
I'd like to drink a toast to you.

695
00:27:17,510 --> 00:27:18,790
You two should drink less.

696
00:27:18,790 --> 00:27:19,920
I'm just happy today.

697
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:21,000
It's a happy occasion. Cheers!

698
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:21,480
Cheers!

699
00:27:23,350 --> 00:27:23,970
It's true.

700
00:27:24,160 --> 00:27:25,880
All these years,
we've really owed so much to Xiaole.

701
00:27:25,880 --> 00:27:29,270
Whenever there's trouble at our home,
he's always here to help.

702
00:27:29,270 --> 00:27:29,880
Xiaole,

703
00:27:29,910 --> 00:27:31,640
we are all very grateful to you.

704
00:27:31,880 --> 00:27:32,520
Come on.

705
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:34,930
I'd like to drink a toast to you too.

706
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:35,640
Okay.

707
00:27:37,880 --> 00:27:38,310
Lan.

708
00:27:38,330 --> 00:27:38,790
Mrs. Yi.

709
00:27:39,030 --> 00:27:39,350
Eat up.

710
00:27:39,350 --> 00:27:40,750
It's the least I could do.

711
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:47,720
Xiaole,

712
00:27:48,310 --> 00:27:49,880
thanks for helping me with my studies.

713
00:27:49,880 --> 00:27:51,340
Let me drink a toast to you.

714
00:27:53,550 --> 00:27:54,550
Speaking of Xuan,

715
00:27:55,110 --> 00:27:56,440
you probably didn't know this
while you were abroad.

716
00:27:56,440 --> 00:27:57,370
Recently,

717
00:27:57,640 --> 00:27:59,300
his grades have skyrocketed.

718
00:27:59,750 --> 00:28:01,720
He should be able to get
into a good university.

719
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:02,640
When it comes to choosing his major,

720
00:28:02,640 --> 00:28:03,960
you can give him some advice.

721
00:28:03,960 --> 00:28:05,800
Of course. He's my brother.

722
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:08,590
Xiaole,

723
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:10,260
you're so kind.

724
00:28:10,270 --> 00:28:11,530
I'll drink this first.

725
00:28:15,550 --> 00:28:16,270
Slow down.

726
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:20,310
Stop drinking the beverage.

727
00:28:20,310 --> 00:28:20,960
Alright.

728
00:28:30,960 --> 00:28:32,400
Come on. Have some food.

729
00:28:32,720 --> 00:28:33,440
Come on.

730
00:28:37,550 --> 00:28:39,150
Let's all raise our glasses.

731
00:28:39,550 --> 00:28:40,680
Congratulations to Lan

732
00:28:40,680 --> 00:28:42,340
on graduating successfully.

733
00:28:42,930 --> 00:28:43,730
Welcome home.

734
00:28:43,750 --> 00:28:44,160
Yeah!

735
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:44,510
Come on.

736
00:28:44,510 --> 00:28:44,880
Come on.

737
00:28:44,880 --> 00:28:45,640
Let's raise our glasses.

738
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:46,170
Cheers!

739
00:28:46,200 --> 00:28:46,910
Cheers.

740
00:28:46,940 --> 00:28:47,510
Cheers.

741
00:28:48,680 --> 00:28:49,880
Cheers.

742
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:51,000
So happy.

743
00:28:57,200 --> 00:28:57,890
Lan.

744
00:28:58,030 --> 00:28:58,510
Yes?

745
00:28:58,590 --> 00:29:00,000
Lan, you and Xiaole

746
00:29:00,480 --> 00:29:03,540
take those pastries
and share them with the neighbors.

747
00:29:03,790 --> 00:29:06,750
Let them have a taste
of our family's cooking.

748
00:29:08,960 --> 00:29:09,510
Mr. Yi,

749
00:29:10,310 --> 00:29:11,000
I can

750
00:29:11,550 --> 00:29:12,610
do this alone.

751
00:29:12,960 --> 00:29:14,720
Just let Lan rest early.

752
00:29:15,510 --> 00:29:17,240
No, that's not what I mean.

753
00:29:17,240 --> 00:29:17,570
No...

754
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:18,480
You...

755
00:29:18,750 --> 00:29:20,080
You and Lan go together.

756
00:29:20,680 --> 00:29:22,080
It has to be the two of you.

757
00:29:23,310 --> 00:29:25,310
Your dad wants the neighbors to know

758
00:29:25,510 --> 00:29:27,040
that you two are doing well.

759
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:39,340
We'll go, then.

760
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,640
Come back soon.

761
00:29:45,070 --> 00:29:45,550
Well,

762
00:29:48,110 --> 00:29:49,070
we're off, Dad.

763
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:55,160
Yi Lan, wait for me!

764
00:29:55,400 --> 00:29:56,350
Okay.

765
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:02,000
Be careful.

766
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:08,240
Dad

767
00:30:08,480 --> 00:30:09,790
can really drink.

768
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:20,540
We've arrived?

769
00:30:21,330 --> 00:30:21,720
Yeah.

770
00:30:21,920 --> 00:30:22,780
We've arrived.

771
00:30:25,070 --> 00:30:26,000
Uncle Li!

772
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:27,160
Uncle Li.

773
00:30:28,480 --> 00:30:29,440
Uncle Li.

774
00:30:30,750 --> 00:30:31,510
Uncle Li!

775
00:30:32,360 --> 00:30:33,190
Uncle Li!

776
00:30:33,720 --> 00:30:34,980
Uncle Li, are you home?

777
00:30:36,240 --> 00:30:37,240
Isn't this Lan?

778
00:30:37,260 --> 00:30:38,240
-Long time no see.
-You're back!

779
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:38,640
Yes.

780
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:39,720
That's great.

781
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:41,880
We neighbors really missed you.

782
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:42,880
I missed you too.

783
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:45,150
My dad made some pastries.

784
00:30:45,330 --> 00:30:46,600
We brought you some specially.

785
00:30:46,600 --> 00:30:47,930
My dad made some pastries.

786
00:30:47,930 --> 00:30:49,660
We brought you some specially.

787
00:30:49,720 --> 00:30:50,200
Oh?

788
00:30:50,640 --> 00:30:52,440
He's calling your dad "Dad" now?

789
00:30:53,630 --> 00:30:54,800
When is the wedding?

790
00:30:54,820 --> 00:30:56,820
We're waiting for the celebration.

791
00:30:58,600 --> 00:30:59,610
Soon...

792
00:31:00,450 --> 00:31:02,510
It's snowing
and you didn't even bring an umbrella.

793
00:31:02,510 --> 00:31:04,240
Wait a moment. I'll get you one.

794
00:31:05,310 --> 00:31:06,440
Thank you, Uncle Li.

795
00:31:06,460 --> 00:31:07,040
Okay.

796
00:31:11,550 --> 00:31:11,960
Hey,

797
00:31:11,960 --> 00:31:13,820
come in and take shelter for a bit.

798
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:33,000
The snow is getting heavier.

799
00:32:04,720 --> 00:32:05,440
Take the umbrella.

800
00:32:05,440 --> 00:32:06,570
Thank you, Uncle Li.

801
00:32:06,580 --> 00:32:08,030
It's snowing hard.

802
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:10,270
Please go back inside. It's cold outside.

803
00:32:10,270 --> 00:32:10,850
Okay.

804
00:32:10,880 --> 00:32:12,030
Be careful on the road.

805
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:12,550
It's slippery.

806
00:32:12,550 --> 00:32:13,240
We're leaving now.

807
00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:13,960
Okay.

808
00:32:19,240 --> 00:32:21,480
Mrs. Wang, we were just coming to see you.

809
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:22,040
Lan,

810
00:32:22,070 --> 00:32:23,320
Xiaole, you're back.

811
00:32:23,400 --> 00:32:24,440
My dad made some pastries.

812
00:32:24,440 --> 00:32:26,000
We were just about to bring them to you.

813
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:28,030
You two are so thoughtful,

814
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:29,960
coming all the way to bring us pastries.

815
00:32:29,960 --> 00:32:31,560
Is today a special occasion?

816
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:33,700
Today is a special day.

817
00:32:35,720 --> 00:32:36,840
Yeah.

818
00:32:37,030 --> 00:32:38,430
Congratulations, then.

819
00:32:38,550 --> 00:32:39,440
It's dark and the roads are slippery.

820
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:40,700
Be careful on your way.

821
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:41,600
I'll be off now.

822
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:42,050
Okay.

823
00:32:42,070 --> 00:32:42,960
-Bye, Mrs. Wang.
-Bye.

824
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:44,200
Bye, Mrs. Wang.

825
00:32:44,200 --> 00:32:44,550
Bye.

826
00:32:48,350 --> 00:32:50,410
Tong Xiaole, what was that nonsense?

827
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:53,720
I didn't say anything wrong.

828
00:32:54,720 --> 00:32:56,170
It's snowing!
